profile.bio: VP of Technology, Womply; formerly Chief Architect, RPX; formerly Sr Director of Eng, Singlefeed; ex-BlackArrow, DHAP Digital, Nickelodeon, etc; musician at Numinous Eye, Collision Stories, ex-SubArachnoid Space; proprieter of Charnel Music; troublemaker.
